==Chinese==
===Mandarin===
[[Pinyin]]: xiù cái yù dào bīng
===Etymology===
First half of the phrase:
*[[秀才]][[遇]][[到]][[兵]] - [[有理]][[說]][[不]][[清]]
*[[秀才]][[遇]][[到]][[兵]] - [[有理]][[说]][[不]][[清]]
Literally: a scholar meets a foot soldier (and cannot not use reason with him)
===Idiom ([[歇後語]], [[歇后语]])===
'''[[秀才]][[遇]][[到]][[兵]]'''
# like talking to a brick wall
